20 (b) Either:
21 a. A diploma and academic transcripts from a school accredited by the Liaison
22 Committee on Medical Education, the Commission on Osteopathic College
23 Accreditation, or a similar accrediting agency; or
24 b. A valid certificate from the Educational Commission for Foreign Medical
25 Graduates (ECFMG); and
26 (c) A certificate demonstrating that the applicant has satisfied the requirements
27 of section 334.035 relating to postgraduate training. An applicant who holds a valid
