30 (2) Except as provided in subsection 3 of this section, the board shall not require
31 applicants to provide information in addition to the information the applicant is
32 required to furnish under this subsection.

SS SCS HCS HB 2372 79
33 2. In determining the qualifications necessary for licensure as a qualified physician
